When multiple lines of text enclosed in \{code\} and pasted into Notepad, carriage returns seem to be lost.

For example, something like this:
{code}
Line 1
Line 2
Line 3
{code}

Will be pasted as:
Line 1 Line 2 Line 3

This behavior is specific to IE (tested with 7 and 8), and does not occur in Firefox or Chrome. Interestingly, text enclosed in \{noformat\} is not affected by this, probably because in the source the text is enclosed in <pre> </pre> tags.

